{"type": "article", "id": 63006, "title": "废弃边角料组合起来，就是一套限量版艺术花瓶｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2019-04-16T22:51:27Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 57941, "name": "Panter & Tourron"}, {"id": 2267, "name": "Longchamp"}, {"id": 43553, "name": "nendo"}, {"id": 242, "name": "YOY"}, {"id": 57886, "name": "KETTAL"}, {"id": 13225, "name": "深泽直人"}, {"id": 52802, "name": "Melanie Abrantes"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 114, "image": "img/article/article_show/20190416210608gdVJ8szBiK5jaTIO.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} span.s4 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><h3>Limited-Edition Marais Vase Collection by Melanie Abrantes</h3><p>在过去的五年里，可持续设计师 Melanie Abrantes 一直在寻找利用手工制作自己产品的剩余材料的方法。</p><p>Melanie Abrantes 没有像许多制造商那样抛弃它们，而是选择了软木和木材，并将它们与抛光的玻璃容器配对。她将软木和木材片层压在一起，然后将它们装配在木材机床上。最终成果是一套限量版花瓶系列。</p><p>每个花瓶都有不同的彩色玻璃、软木和硬木组合，这些组合元素搭配在一起，成为一种功能性艺术品。整套售价 175 美元，<a href=\"https://melanieabrantes.shop/products/marais-vase-collection\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190416210649deVmz9aQbnwRxg45.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.510156\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190416210649JnGREae7KH21ANqC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.497656\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190416210650W5HTE8m1zM46JyB9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.533594\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190416210650CTU1JzLlSIEyu7Bi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.571094\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190416210651nQM6dj9OyACwqWfG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.596875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190416210651Mh9n3KAGrPqy5Bkp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667188\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190416210651NjwL6z0IEoB792Vd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Half Dome Lamp by Naoto Fukasawa for KETTAL</h3><p>最近，家具品牌 KETTAL 请来日本设计师深泽直人（Naoto Fukasawa），设计了一款半圆拱形的落地灯。</p><p>半圆顶落地灯就像是一座大山，能够散发出无穷无尽的各种氛围的灯光，与天空和四季的光线交相辉映。</p><p>这种落地灯看似有些冷淡，但实际上却能够适应各种空间环境，并与其产生创造性的空间氛围。半圆顶落地灯的直径不大不小正合适，跟人们想象中的月亮一般大小。因此，当它被安置在室外空间时，灯泡和半圆顶形状的灯罩悬挂在灯架上，就像是悬在夜空中的月亮。</p><p>这个半圆拱形的落地灯由金属铝打造而成，有两种灯架样式和 34 种颜色。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190416210753QLt5oxJAUXDwneCi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190416210753WzJ2Q0shUGSLEZ6m.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190416210754M4yXxbjV5qzUpdAm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190416210754nteqPdG0ZzBRxiyc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190416210755bci0E6MnLYfSmjtp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190416210755n2ZEDrTFHe6XCocK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.kettal.com%24/\" rel=\"nofollow\">KETTAL</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>OBJECT by YOY</h3><p>在 2019 米兰设计周的 EXISTENCE 展览上，日本设计工作室 YOY 推出了一款名为 OBJECT 的壁灯。</p><p>它形似一个装在墙上的放东西的架子。设计师将 LED 灯和灯罩结构放置在 40 毫米厚的架子内，使用者可以将物件放在架子内，通过投影的方式将物件的影子投射在壁灯后方的墙壁上。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190416210859veHb5ICxGijoRakn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190416210859WDdlrK35FO28UfSC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190416210900EBnOiCW7kyxSo4Gq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190416210900KWLYV9ilACfI4tso.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190416210901ZMcFUfrR9XBoN02y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201904162109017waE4Y0vG6zjrCiO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>katachi collection by Nendo for  Longchamp</h3><p>katachi collection 是日本设计工作室 Nendo 为法国奢华包袋品牌 Longchamp 设计的新手袋系列。Longchamp 品牌最具代表性的 Le Pliage 手袋系列以日本折纸手工为灵感，凭借其轻巧的结构和便于折叠的形式很受欢迎。</p><p>katachi collection 手袋系列的设计在延续原有理念的同时又新加入了方形、圆锥和平面圆形三种新款式，既可以作为随身携带的手袋，又可以折叠或卷起来放置在住宅不同地方另作他用。在使用时，手袋可以根据需要装入的物品来调整大小，因此它功能灵活，既能够折叠成小巧的形状收纳起来又能够调整成为可供使用的最大容量。</p><p>方形手袋借助可拆卸的底垫保持自身几何形状，是房间内可以灵活使用的储物盒。三角圆锥形手袋能够很方便的挂在衣帽钩上，可以放置在衣柜或架子上用来收纳小件配饰。由于顶部采用了圆锥形皮革，手袋即使在悬挂时候也可以很轻松地打开来取放物品。圆形的手袋类似日本的风吕敷，可以折叠平整存放。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201904162109325UdVLhz4m6B8s3In.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667708\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190416210932K6Dofhqu8AO1l3L4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667708\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190416210932Y7gMFB3WHektvKRq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667708\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201904162109324fi5QTNSAbKZ93pw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667708\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190416210933AvOq3o1LenjG6C7c.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667708\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2019041621093315tZUPvQ8rBDzFwX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667708\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190416210933SICGhwqueKVlHcD6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667708\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201904162109339IaCjNG2ZWs4rASm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667708\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2019041621093448nDjXNzRxb91YO5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667708\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190416210934LfyAPZTNFrmHSWRE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667708\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190416210934uoFkl3PSWRhs4nBb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667708\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.nendo.jp/en/works/katachi-collection/?erelease\" rel=\"nofollow\">Nendo</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Tense Collection by Panter &amp; Tourron</h3><p>洛桑设计工作室 Panter＆Tourron 的 Tense 系列是一套平板式家具，重量不到 20 千克，可以在任何地方轻松组装。</p><p>米兰设计周期间，Tense 系列在 Via Popoli Uniti 的 Alcova 展览空间展出，这个五件套系列是一个研究项目，旨在为移动一代寻找创新的家具解决方案。</p><p>它包括一张桌子、椅子、吊灯、带照明功能的镜子和可用于划分空间的隔断。所有部件都非常轻巧。</p><p>每一款产品都是平板式包装，方便运输，并且可以在不需要零件或工具的情况下进行组装。桌子非常耐用，桌面由再生塑料薄片制成，放在相同材料的中空圆形鼓底座上。这两个元件用一条塑料带固定在一起，塑料带固定在底座下面。整个桌子重量不到 5 千克，不需要螺丝。</p><p>空间隔断是用和制作耐克编织款运动鞋相同的材料制成，重量仅为 1.2 千克。无纺纸灯的重量仅为 250 克，并在两个连接的纸盘内装有 LED 灯条。它既防水也不会撕裂，可以卷起来放在管子里。</p><p>圆形镜子具有可弯曲的丙烯酸边缘，覆盖有二向色膜，以产生彩色效果。像灯一样，它也可以用管子运输，设计师认为这样可以降低运输成本。</p><p>团队认为轻量化是可持续发展的未来，污染较少，而且运输费用较少。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190416211029QUe52GhR9gNnXPO6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190416211030rgnOa6izoBhmDbJU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201904162110322PLX7tYGoMipeTzN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190416211033HiXPuQz7FI3TvfZR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190416211035rAYK3TVI24umUxyS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190416211036ChRUiKnQlZXbHJIF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190416211038F5qcx2bs36w8PRCJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562606\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201904162110382GL3pQ6bgcNjyADP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190416211039yT6oF5BXn9DA3tE7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://pantertourron.com/work/tense/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Panter &amp; Tourron</a></figcaption></figure></div><p class=\"\"><br></p>"}